  "title": "Basic Editing",
  "content": "Adjust is a panel for basic image editing, covering light, exposure, vibrance, saturation, vignette, and other look controls. Use it when you want quick manual slider tuning.\n\nCrop lets you reframe an image by keeping only the area you want. Drag to define the region, enter exact width and height values, or pick a preset aspect ratio.\n\nFlip mirrors an image across its horizontal or vertical axis.\n\nRotate turns an image by a chosen angle, either in 90° increments or by a custom value.",
